553
00:57:56.944 --> 00:57:58.846
- You're insane.

554
00:58:01.415 --> 00:58:03.351
- Let me show you.

555
00:58:03.451 --> 00:58:05.152
[metal clangs]

556
00:58:05.252 --> 00:58:12.193
♪ ♪

557
00:58:18.165 --> 00:58:24.038
It's taken us 20 years
