561
00:58:35.016 --> 00:58:36.083
- No.

562
00:58:36.183 --> 00:58:38.386
These are all our failures.

563
00:58:38.486 --> 00:58:42.857
What's inside you
is our success.

564
00:58:42.957 --> 00:58:49.830
♪ ♪

565
00:58:49.930 --> 00:58:55.002
I left the field of genetics
because some people

566
